Horse simulator coursework for ECS414U (object-oriented programming).

Started 19 Apr 2024.

Part 1: text-based simulator (in textual branch)
To compile:
`javac ./Horse.class`
To run:
`java Horse`

Part 2: graphical-based simulator (in graphical branch -> main)
To compile:
`javac ./Simulator.java`
To run:
`java Simulator`

Ensure all files are downloaded and in the same folder.
- Simulator.java
- Horse.java
- Race.java
- Track.java

Upon running, user will be greeted with an option to design a track, to successfully initiate a race:
- create at least 1 track
- create at least 3 horses
- click start race

